sources.description:
*Aquarium Of The Dead* - Workers at an aquarium off the coast of southern California find themselves surrounded by undead marine life after a mysterious virus sweeps through the building. Only steps from an ocean inlet, the workers must fight to stop the creatures before they escape into the sea and infect the entire planet. 
2021.  Stars: Vivica A. Fox, Eva Ceja, D.C. Douglas
